This paper deals with improving the performance of virtualized cluster servers through intelligent decision making, which involves load balancing and VM migration. This topic falls under the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of Multi Criteria Decision Making techniques, which is related to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of Web Services and File Services, which are related to the Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of virtualization, which is related to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. Finally, the paper mentions the use of algorithms, which is related to the Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-category.
